  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (W-AR-05 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment: 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). This package contains a targeted W-AR-05 defeater: the primary validation result omits a comparedAgainst link, and the secondary validation result references an experimental comparator whose operating flow regime (ventricular assist, not CPB) does not match the declared COU, though the mismatch is discussed only in positive terms.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cpb-hemolysis-rh-criterion",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cfd-identifies-worstcase-hemolysis-cpb",
