      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) holds a current FDA-recognised software quality certificate; version control log and regression test suite documented in SQA-2025-001.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 is used under a validated installation with documented version control, regression testing, and change management procedures consistent with MRL 2 requirements. SQA record SQA-2025-001 confirms all required controls are in place."
