      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Benchmark test cases (lid-driven cavity, Hagen-Poiseuille pipe flow) reproduce analytical solutions to within 0.5% at the mesh densities used in production runs.",
      "rationale": "Standard benchmark verification cases were executed at solver installation and at each major version update. Residuals and solution norms confirm correct implementation of the governing equations. Gradation 1 is sufficient at MRL 2."
    },
    {
