      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; single representative pump specimen used for validation.",
      "rationale": "A single pump specimen representative of nominal manufacturing tolerances was used for in-vitro validation. Statistical characterisation of specimen-to-specimen variability is not required at MRL 2 for this factor."
