    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40-2018 requirements table for Class II devices with Medium model influence and High decision consequence. Primary validation achieved MAE=8.3% against the pre-specified 15% threshold. Secondary validation against Fraser 2012 provided independent corroboration (R²=0.94, NRMSE=6.1%). The assessment team concluded that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device.",
